              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42973161/" class="">11. 战败中的复活者</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48191747/" class=" " title="Fiasco">Fiasco</a>
              
                <span class="allstar10" title="很差"></span>
